{"tid":1006735,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"地區團體屯門示威　籲內地客返回深圳辦年貨","createTime":"2019-02-03T08:08:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T10:36:09.000Z","uid":20816,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"94df78c380d8d347b7bff1c6b5a17f7f5f7661e1","tid":1006735,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T08:08:45.000Z","msg":"大約十名關注水貨活動的人士在屯門示威，呼籲來港辦年貨的內地居民，返回內地購物。<br />\n<br />\n發起行動的團體之一、「屯門兆翠關注組」召集人甄霈霖表示，大批內地自由行旅客到屯門區購買日常用品，已對當區居民造成滋擾，亦推高附近商店的物價和租金。<br />\n<br />\n本身是屯門居民的甄霈霖說，明白內地遊客對本港商店的貨品有信心，但深圳南山區亦有本港商店的分店，因此他們在農曆新年前到屯門B3X巴士站，呼籲經深圳灣來港的自由行旅客，返回深圳辦年貨。他強調行動會和平進行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1441340-20190203.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1441340-20190203.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=6VpbUQS5Cy4QwgKrD6%2Fp7q7XYz%2BrpCtmef%2B4BlhZTRs%3D&h=393d04f6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1441340-20190203.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7ec5f1bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1441340-20190203.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"594e6be64b586d0ab8ec92f0ea4c028413162d3b","tid":1006735,"uid":174420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T08:09:36.000Z","msg":"十名<br />\n我睇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acf763830996b8865ca920df5b4ceccb37cce76f","tid":1006735,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"594e6be64b586d0ab8ec92f0ea4c028413162d3b","tid":1006735,"uid":174420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T08:09:36.000Z","msg":"十名<br />\n我睇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T08:10:34.000Z","msg":"港台數錯"},{"pid":"f3a27d0947511121c15cd3af36095f50a020c89d","tid":1006735,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime